name: Extensions
tagline: Creating and uploading several extensions under this repository.
body:
### Welcome to Extensions repo.
This site is only for uploading browser extensions for Google Chrome, Firefox and Safari.

### Authors and Contributors
In 2015, Ranganadh Paramkusam (@vssranganadhp) created 'extensions' repo.

### Support or Contact
If you've any issue when using these extensions, feel free to create an issue on it.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
